---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const benefits = [
  { title: 'Corrosion Resistant', description: 'Unlike iron fences, aluminum does not corrode over time. Built to last through Pittsburgh weather.' },
  { title: 'Customizable', description: 'Choose your preferred color, height, and finish to match your property.' },
  { title: 'Low Maintenance', description: 'Resistant to peeling, corrosion, and flaking. Requires fewer repairs than other fence types.' },
  { title: 'Quick Installation', description: 'Can be installed quickly, even on inclines like hillsides.' },
  { title: 'Versatile', description: 'Great for residential and commercial properties, pool enclosures, and more.' },
  { title: 'Adds Value', description: 'An attractive deterrent to trespassing that defines property lines and adds curb appeal.' },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Aluminum Fence Installation - Affordable Fence & Railing, LLC"
  description="Expert aluminum fence installations for residential and commercial properties in Pittsburgh, PA. Corrosion-resistant, customizable, and low maintenance. Free estimates."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-muted py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Our Products</p>
        <h1>Aluminum Fence Installations in Pittsburgh, PA</h1>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 text-lg mt-6 leading-relaxed">
          Durable, low-maintenance aluminum fencing for residential and commercial properties. Customizable color, height, and finish.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-6">What Are Aluminum Fences?</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Affordable Fence & Railing provides aluminum fence installations for residential and commercial properties. Aluminum fencing is a durable, low-maintenance type of fence that is available in various styles, and we are proud to offer the best selection of aluminum fences in town. Unlike traditional iron fences, aluminum fences do not corrode over time. You can customize your fence by specifying the color, height, and finish.
          </p>
          <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Aluminum fences are typically used to keep unwanted visitors out of an area while not completely concealing the area. The average aluminum fence comprises dark vertical bars with space in between. These fences are comparatively affordable, versatile, and low maintenance. They are a great choice for anyone that wants to protect their property.
          </p>
          <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You have probably seen an aluminum fence surrounding a public pool or golf course. Aluminum fences are a common choice for properties meant to entice rather than discourage visitors. Due to their resilient nature, these fences require fewer repairs and less maintenance than other fences.
          </p>
          <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
            Affordable Fence & Railing is a trusted provider of fencing materials, which allows you to undergo DIY projects with confidence. We also perform aluminum fencing installations for whatever project you may need. If you want to be confident that your fence was installed professionally and reliably, ask us about our installation services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <img
            src="/images/gettyimages-1139142927-1920w.jpg"
            alt="Aluminum Fence in Pittsburgh, PA"
            class="rounded-lg w-full"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/img_2036-640w-1920w.webp"
            alt="Aluminum Fence Around Pool"
            class="rounded-lg w-full"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits -->
  <section class="bg-muted py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-14">
        <p class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Benefits</p>
        <h2>Why Choose Aluminum Fence</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {benefits.map((benefit, i) => (
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-primary/20 leading-none">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base mb-2">{benefit.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">{benefit.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery Row -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <img src="/images/505-640w-1920w.webp" alt="Black Painted Aluminum Fence" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/img_2047-640w-1920w.webp" alt="Fence Made of Steel" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/img_2119-640w-1920w.webp" alt="Black Fence and Gate of a House" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-primary/5 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Get an Aluminum Fence Quote</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Find more information on our aluminum fence installation and fabrication service when you call our team in Pittsburgh, PA, for a free estimate.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">
          Request a Free Estimate
        </a>
        <a href="tel:412-766-1464" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 border-2 border-primary/30 text-primary font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">
          Call 412-766-1464
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
